BRK | Company Profile 




 




Welcome to BRK, your one source for residential safety products.Our full line includes smoke alarms, carbon monoxide alarms, heat alarms, fire extinguishers, relays, motion sensors and fire escape ladders. To find out more, click on the "Products" tab above and view our product listings.  For over 50 years we’ve made the home safety products that make your job easier.You can install BRK Brands, Inc. products with confidence! Our products are designed to save lives. It's a responsibility we don't take lightly. We build each smoke alarm, carbon monoxide alarm, heat alarm, and fire extinguisher to the highest standards. Over the years we've seen competitors come and go. We're still here, still making the most recognized consumer brands of smoke and CO alarms on the market. Our brands include BRK®, First Alert®, Family Gard®, Tundra® and OneLink®. We have also taken a leadership role in building the home safety product category, and in educating communities on making their homes safer. We partner with Fire Services Professionals, schools, and other community groups to promote prevention and fire and CO safety, and we help our distributors through point-of-purchase sales tools and special seasonal promotions. We are totally committed to serving our customers, from you - the professionals who install our products - to the families who count on them. We are proud of the products we make, and welcome the opportunity to serve all our customers together.


 



 







