on GlobeNewswire





BRK INC. (OTCBB: BRKK) Completes Purchase of Broadcast Helmet Camera System Technology


Aug. 4, 2016 at 2:41 a.m. ET
on ACCESSWIRE











BRK Inc.


            
            BRK, Inc. is engaged in the development and distribution of vertical blind repair kit. Its products consists of plastic mold that provides invisible repairs for vertical blinds and allows the owner to extend the life of the blind vane and eliminates the need to special order or replace blinds due to damage. The company was founded on May 22, 2008 and is headquartered in Las Vegas, NV.

            
            (See Full Profile)


  



 
   






   



























